{"title":"Rhodoks的取数游戏","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["2020寒假入门课程","贪心"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1130#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/submissions?problem_id=1130","statistics":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1130/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1130/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/discussion/problem/1130"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$\\text{Rhodoks}$掏出了一个数集给JM和qz做游戏。规则如下：\r\n\r\n1. JM只允许取奇数。\r\n\r\n2. qz只允许取偶数。\r\n\r\n3. 双方轮流取数，如果某人不能取数，游戏结束。\r\n\r\n4. 先手的人选可以自由选择。\r\n\r\nJM和qz有着共同的目标，就是使最终集合里剩下的数的和最小。由于他们非常懒惰不想思考，他们把你抓来解决这个问题，如果你无法解决就会被qz吃掉。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行一个正整数 $n$ 。\r\n\r\n接下来一行 $n$ 个整数 $a_i$ ，代表数集中的数。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一个整数，代表集合里剩下的数的和的最小值。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入1\r\n```plain\r\n5\r\n1 2 3 4 5\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出1\r\n```plain\r\n0\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输入2\r\n```plain\r\n3\r\n1 1 1\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出2\r\n```plain\r\n2\r\n```\r\n\r\n"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1 \\leq n \\leq 2000$\r\n\r\n$1 \\leq a_i \\leq 10^6$"}]}